  [Documentation]
  - Added INSTALL file to the distribution.

  [Toolchain]
  - Tweaks to dist.ini for simplifying build.

  [Other]
  - Remove cruft from distribution.

v0.2.0    2018-10-18 23:14:52+01:00 Europe/London
